feat: add UTXO-DNS pluggable multi-chain wallet SDK

This PR introduces a modular, pluggable wallet SDK with:

- Core type definitions (AddressBook, TEEDomainAssertion, UTXO, etc.)
- Pluggable DNS resolution (UTXO-DNS gateway, ENS subdomain EIP-3668)
- Pluggable TEE backends (Intel SGX, mock for development)
- Multi-chain transaction building (Bitcoin UTXO model)
- vLEI compliance module (GLEIF integration)
- IPv6 color fingerprint visualization
- Local storage with memory cache
- Unified Wallet SDK entry point

All components follow interface-based design for easy replacement.

Design references:
- Ethereum Foundation IPTF PoCs TEE demo
- Aegis Solana TEE proxy key托管 design
- Go multi-chain wallet PSBT transaction building
- GLEIF vLEI credential standard

